      "created": "2014-11-25T19:28:41.783+0000",
      "description": "HDFS is tracing using htrace now, as are other applications including HBase and Accumulo.  It would be a nice feature if we enabled writing traces to the timeline server.  I envision an htrace SpanReceiver implementation that uses the TimelineClient to store tracing data.  The htrace API may end up being a more convenient way to instrument applications to store timeline data in the timeline server.",
